    <bug_when>2013-06-25 13:56:25 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Markdown parser emits gratuitous newlines &apos;\n&apos; when parsing content.  Newlines should not be emitted gratuitously after inline HTML or when closing a paragraph, since these end up as significant content in the output.</thetext>
  </long_desc><long_desc isprivate="0" >
