    <who name="Stefan Seelmann">mail</who>
    <bug_when>2013-06-25 14:32:49 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>I added those newlines because the available Markdown implementations (markdown.pl, Python, PHP) also add newlines (sometimes even two) to the HTML output. But I agree that it isn&apos;t required to add such line breaks, and the Wikitext framework is also not a pure MD-to-HTML converter.</thetext>
